Spotify Playlist Creator



3. https://animechan.vercel.app/api/random      -  get random anime characterb quote
1. https://accounts.spotify.com/authorize       - send authorize request, and redirect to /receive-code
1. https://accounts.spotify.com/api/token       - request access token using authorization token

2. api.spotify.com/v1/me                       - get user profile, need spotify id in it to send create playlist request
4. https://api.spotify.com/v1/users/${spotifyID}/playlists        - send create playlist request